premise_source_doc_sentence: The film received negative reviews , despite gaining a moderate return at the box office grossing $ 57 million worldwide , and it was considered a disappointment compared to the previous film 's $ 98 million gross on a smaller production budget .

The studio 's highest-grossing films are Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles  (  2014  )  , which grossed $ 493.3 million worldwide , The Adventures of Tintin  (  2011  )  , which grossed $ 374 million worldwide , and
Part 2 has grossed $ 281 million in North America , with a total of $ 652 million worldwide .

The first installment , Divergent  (  2014  )  , grossed over $ 288 million worldwide , while the second installment , The Divergent Series : Insurgent  (  2015  )  , grossed over $ 297 million worldwide .
